k" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BA%ADu-xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-pPfm04Ndb1ofigs2tCoNVQ">Hậu xuất tái kỳ 4 - 後出塞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-B%C3%ACnh-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-th%C3%A0nh-Phi%C3%AAn-S%E1%BB%A9-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Trang-Ho%C3%A0ng-Ki%C3%AAm-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-thuy%C3%AAn-th%C4%83ng-H%C3%A0-T%C4%A9nh-tu%E1%BA%A7n-ph%E1%BB%A7-l%C6%B0u/poem-pNK05RAt_HtR3yW1oIEuhw">Hoạ Quảng Bình đồng thành Phiên Sứ Ngọc Trang Hoàng Kiêm tiên sinh thuyên thăng Hà Tĩnh tuần phủ lưu giản nguyên vận kỳ 1 - 和廣平同城藩使玉莊黃兼先生銓陞河靜巡撫留柬原韻其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/L%E1%BA%A1c-th%E1%BA%A7n-ph%C3%BA/poem-ylYQnboi4bp_70hzYu0a0Q">Lạc thần phú - 洛神賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/M%E1%BB%99ng-du-Thi%C3%AAn-M%E1%BB%A5-ng%C3%A2m-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-xYeOxFf3_7JKfRJV6fVL9w">Mộng du Thiên Mụ ngâm lưu biệt - 夢遊天姥吟留別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Ngu%E1%BB%B5-l%E1%BB%A5c-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-chi-Giao-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng/poem-exlRb_wJFewa90nBwMrF8A">Phụng tặng Nguỵ lục trượng hữu thiếu phủ chi Giao Quảng - 奉送魏六丈佑少府之交廣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
